WEBVTT

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:31.816
Talk to Black Lives Matter
and the police union about that.

00:12:31.840 --> 00:12:33.536
We need to tackle this.

00:12:33.560 --> 00:12:38.280
(Applause)

00:12:40.640 --> 00:12:42.136
At the end of the day,

00:12:42.160 --> 00:12:44.896
perhaps people won't feel the need

00:12:44.920 --> 00:12:47.656
to buy and use a gun

00:12:47.680 --> 00:12:52.496
when they all equally feel safe,

00:12:52.520 --> 00:12:56.280
healthy, respected and cared for.

00:12:58.080 --> 00:13:00.216
All right, discussion time is over.